                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-92-off540 t18281023-92-cd541"></join>, 1 bag, value 6d.; 1 purse, value 6d.; 2 half-crowns, 1 shilling, 1 sixpence, and 7 1/2d. in copper monies, the property of 
